session_summary: Jolene and Deborah conversed at 7:03 pm on 1 February, 2023. Jolene shared about her challenging but fun robotics project that tests her creativity and problem-solving skills. Deborah praised her and asked about her feelings when she first received the project. Jolene felt a mix of excitement and nerves initially but now enjoys working on it, comparing it to solving a puzzle and finding designing and programming solutions. Deborah met her new neighbor at yoga in the park and they discussed the benefits of yoga in their lives. Jolene mentioned planning to play console games with her partner instead of resuming yoga. Deborah acknowledged the importance of having shared activities with her partner. The conversation ended with Jolene saying goodbye and looking forward to meeting again.

conversation_turns.blip_caption: a photo of a table with a robot on it and a laptop
conversation_turns.text: Hi Deb! How're you? I've been busy. My engineering professor gave us a huge robotics project. It's tough but fun, it's making me get creative and problem-solve.

conversation_turns.speaker: Deborah
conversation_turns.text: Hey Jolene! It's great to hear from you. It sounds challenging but interesting! It must be really putting your creative and problem-solving skills to the test. How did you feel when you first received the project? Are you enjoying working on it?

conversation_turns.speaker: Jolene
conversation_turns.text: When I got it, I felt a mix of emotions - excited and nervous. But now, I'm really enjoying it! It's like trying to solve a puzzle, figuring out the best design and programming. Seeing the robot come together is awesome too!

conversation_turns.speaker: Deborah
conversation_turns.blip_caption: a photo of a yellow sign with a picture of a family
conversation_turns.text: That's awesome, Jolene! You're enjoying the process. It must be really satisfying to see it come together. Keep up the good work! Oh, by the way, I met my new neighbor Anna yesterday!

conversation_turns.speaker: Deborah
conversation_turns.text: It happened at yoga in the park.

conversation_turns.speaker: Jolene
conversation_turns.text: Wow, that's awesome! It's great connecting with people who have similar interests. Did you two talk about it?

conversation_turns.speaker: Deborah
conversation_turns.text: Yeah, we talked about how it has improved our lives and the sense of community it gives.

conversation_turns.speaker: Jolene
conversation_turns.blip_caption: a photo of a purse with a plant on a table

conversation_turns.speaker: Deborah
conversation_turns.text: Have you ever thought about resuming yoga?

conversation_turns.speaker: Jolene
conversation_turns.text: Well... we planned to play the console with my partner.

conversation_turns.speaker: Deborah
conversation_turns.text: It's also good that you have something to do together.
